\v 5 Ngiyilindele iN\nd kosi\x + Hlab. 40.1. Isa. 26.8. Hlab. 27.14.\x*\nd*, umphefumulo wami ulindile\x + Hlab. 33.20.\x*, lelizwini layo ngiyathemba\x + Hlab. 119.74.\x*.
\v 6 Umphefumulo wami \add ulindela\add* iNkosi okwedlula abalindele\x + Hlab. 63.6.\x* ukusa, belindele ukusa\x + Hlab. 5.3.\x*.
