\v 7 UIsrayeli kathembele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Hlab. 131.3.\x*; ngoba eN\nd kosi\nd*ni kulothandolomusa, njalo kuyo kulohlengo olunengi\x + Hlab. 86.15.\x*.
\v 8 Yona-ke izahlenga uIsrayeli kuzo zonke iziphambeko zakhe\x + Hlab. 25.22. Hlab. 103.3.\x*.
